{"tid":285141,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)銀髮阿基德 綠里奇蹟  特務型戰","createTime":"2017-06-15T14:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T19:50:01.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2198f4f91de80d222a633d4e6654eec20713589e","tid":285141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=4qFxAY7fLlGHiWDXwGBX%2F%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ef293a1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=4qFxAY7fLlGHiWDXwGBX%2F%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=79167787\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=4qFxAY7fLlGHiWDXwGBX%2F%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=142d6c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/weitzern/1186559745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fweitzern%2F1186559745.jpg&h=a4340335&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/ce/Green_mile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fce%2FGreen_mile.jpg&h=bd4e9b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/01/The_Man_from_U.N.C.L.E._Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F01%2FThe_Man_from_U.N.C.L.E._Poster.jpg&h=221fe847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.300年後的未來（2306年），因為遺傳基因實驗失敗，產生了有思想的森林，變得襲擊人類和城市化的世界。其中有一個比較與森林友好的中立城市，就是主角阿基德生活的地方。偶然在一次偷取儲水（水在那個世界是最貴重的）的行動中，阿基德遇到在永久生命維持裝置中從沉睡中醒覺的楚拉。阿基德把她救醒，並與她成為朋友，卻萬料不到，原來這一位來自過去的女孩，身懷一個特殊任務&mdash;&mdash;就是要毀滅一切，把地球回復到過去！唯阿基德和朋友卻不苟同，他們渴望走出未來..<br />\n<br />\n2.綠色奇蹟講述年老的保羅（Paul Edgecombe）在老人院中說給一位老婦人朋友聽有關自己在1935年夏天他在死牢當主管的故事。他工作的死牢中監房到死囚室之間的最後一程路上鋪上綠色油漆，所以死囚們稱這段路為「綠色里程」（green mile），而死刑用的電椅就名為「老火花」..<br />\n<br />\n3.故事背景定於1960年代的冷戰時期，美國中央情報局（CIA）特務拿破崙&middot;蘇洛（亨利&middot;卡維爾飾）和蘇聯國安局（KGB）特務伊利亞&middot;科里亞金（艾米&middot;漢默飾）被迫合作，阻止一個神秘的國際犯罪組織 「T.H.R.U.S.H.[註 1]」，原來這個組織是納粹餘黨，他們綁架了一名核武專家泰勒博士（克里斯丁&middot;伯克飾），意圖引爆第三次世界大戰，蘇洛與科里亞金找到了專家住在東柏林的愛女蓋比&middot;泰勒（艾莉西亞&middot;薇坎德飾），偕往羅馬尋找泰勒博士，將核彈沒收，以阻止核災的發生；但其實蓋比早被英國軍情六處（MI6）招募..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277a542be3c47f5f9a3a7de59b150d0372528b91","tid":285141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89760cdec8e1f7ace269177054673d519bbcab1","tid":285141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febffe2ace86383e19f577240e4c23819903b1cf","tid":285141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f015cc7aa8f20c91cc84ab1051eb207143995f","ti